ChatGPT said:

Here’s a crisp, beginner-friendly primer you can use today.

What mindfulness is

Paying attention, on purpose, to the present moment—with curiosity and without judging what you notice. The “training” is gently returning your attention every time it wanders.

How to sit

  • Chair or cushion, spine upright but not rigid.

  • Feet flat
